'''硫氰酸铯'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为CsSCN。

==制备及性质==
它可由[[氢氧化铯|氢氧化铯]]和[[硫氰酸铵|硫氰酸铵]]的反应制备<ref>{{cite journal|title=The conductivity of thiocyanates methyl alcohol|journal=Proceedings of the Royal Society of London. Series A, Containing Papers of a Mathematical and Physical Character|volume=127|issue=804|year=1997|pages=228–240|issn=0950-1207|doi=10.1098/rspa.1930.0053}}</ref>，或由[[硫氰酸|硫氰酸]]和[[碳酸铯|碳酸铯]]反应制得。它在210 °C熔化，在空气中加热至500~620 °C按下式分解：<ref name=PB>{{cite journal|last1=Ptaszyński|first1=B.|last2=Skiba|first2=E.|last3=Krystek|first3=J.|title=Thermal decomposition of alkali metal, copper(I) and silver(I) thiocyanates|journal=Thermochimica Acta|volume=319|issue=1-2|year=1998|pages=75–85|issn=00406031|doi=10.1016/S0040-6031(98)00391-8}}</ref>

: 2 CsSCN + 5 O<sub>2</sub> → Cs<sub>2</sub>SO<sub>4</sub> + SO<sub>2</sub> + 2 CO<sub>2</sub> + N<sub>2</sub>

它和四氢噻吩氯化亚金在[[乙腈|乙腈]]中反应，得到Cs[Au(SCN)<sub>2</sub>]。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Coker|first1=Nathan L.|last2=Krause Bauer|first2=Jeanette A.|last3=Elder|first3=R. C.|title=Emission Energy Correlates with Inverse of Gold−Gold Distance for Various [Au(SCN)<sub>2</sub>]<sup>−</sup> Salts|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=126|issue=1|year=2004|pages=12–13|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/ja037012f}}</ref>它和[[草酸铯|草酸铯]]与[[硒酸铀酰|硒酸铀酰]]反应，得到单斜晶系的Cs[UO<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)(NCS)]·{{frac|2}}H<sub>2</sub>O晶体。<ref>Medrish, I. V.; Peresypkina, E. V.; Virovets, A. V.; Serezhkina, L. B. Synthesis and structure of M[UO<sub>2</sub>(C<sub>2</sub>O<sub>4</sub>)​(NCS)​]​·0.5H<sub>2</sub>O (M = Rb or Cs). ''Zhurnal Neorganicheskoi Khimii'', 2008. 53 (7): 1121-1126. ISSN: 0044-457X.</ref>
